<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <title>About TFH MedSpa & Lounge</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        .about-section { padding: 80px 0; background: #0a0a0a; color: #fff; }
        .about-grid { 
            display: grid; 
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; 
            gap: 50px; 
            align-items: center; 
        }
        .about-text h1 { color: #d9f110; font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 20px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .about-text p { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #ccc; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .highlight { color: #d9f110; font-weight: bold; }
        .about-image img { 
            width: 100%; 
            border-radius: 20px; 
            border: 1px solid #d9f110; 
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(217, 241, 16, 0.2); 
        }
        .stats-bar { 
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: space-around; 
            margin-top: 50px; 
            background: #111; 
            padding: 30px; 
            border-radius: 15px; 
            border: 1px solid #222;
        }
        .stat-item h2 { color: #d9f110; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .stat-item p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #888; text-transform: uppercase; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <section class="about-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-grid">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <h1>The TFH Story</h1>
                    <p>Welcome to <span class="highlight">TFH MedSpa and Skin Therapy</span>, Abuja's premier destination where elite wellness meets sophisticated social experiences. We were founded on a singular vision: to create a space where clinical skin expertise and premium relaxation coexist.</p>
                    
                    <p>As a dedicated <span class="highlight">Skin Therapy Hub</span>, we specialize in advanced medical-grade treatments designed to restore your natural glow. From revitalizing facials to professional body polishing, our experts use only high-quality products that deliver real results.</p>
                    
                    <p>But the experience doesn't end with skincare. Our <span class="highlight">Luxury Lounge</span> provides a sanctuary for Abuja's elite to unwind, enjoy premium refreshments, and engage in a friendly game of snooker in an atmosphere of pure class.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="/images/frontveiw3.jpg" alt="TFH MedSpa Front View">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="stats-bar">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h2>100%</h2>
                    <p>Skin Health</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h2>Elite</h2>
                    <p>Lounge Vibes</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h2>Pro</h2>
                    <p>Therapists</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>